  Locus:
    Page: 377
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Prayer
---
I have resolved to pray more and pray always; to pray in all places where
quietness inviteth, in the house, on the highway and on the street, and
know no street or passage in the city that may not witness that I have not
forgotten God.
